[0-8] The security lock is now locked, and the door is open a crack. A hand reaches in with a piece of silver tape and sticks it to the wall, with a rubber band attached to the bottom of the tape. Then the rubber band is looped over the door lock, the door is closed, and the lock automatically falls off, opening the door.
